{"tid":446991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"必理痛度廣告條友係咪同香港人有仇？","createTime":"2017-10-25T00:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T06:47:12.000Z","uid":109462,"like":1367,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"348d94ff5d38df76b7a32abfcd65994a43af5baa","tid":446991,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:22:50.000Z","msg":"成日見到必理痛依家條廣告係惡死老細屌鳩班病到七彩嘅員工，逼佢哋食藥繼續頂，員工怕殘留怕副作用就又比個老細屌；另一條就係女上司見下屬病到五顏六色就死咁款，就串柒柒敲枱叫個細嘅入房掉盒藥比佢食。<br />\n<br />\n當一個人病到唔食藥唔得嘅時候，唔係好應該休息嘅咩？點解必理痛啲廣告可以鼓吹食藥頂硬上呢種不健康風氣？度廣告條友係咪同香港人有仇？"},{"pid":"8a2c493c8de75a3c47b4b959ed04e0ba48757699","tid":446991,"uid":41245,"like":430,"dislike":37,"score":393,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:26:09.000Z","msg":"香港人本身就同香港人有仇<br />\n日日屌香港人係港豬係蝗同支那人冇分別，又話女人係雞，拍YouTube又話低質，打拳又話人造假，唔用支那寶又落後"},{"pid":"7ab96500be0f9402d539e4617da20748c866df51","tid":446991,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:34:22.000Z","msg":"對香港啲廣告撚無期望"},{"pid":"1744cb8256f22012d34a66fcd1f3b4e525287147","tid":446991,"uid":95,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:37:05.000Z","msg":"一齊死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48b3a2e52583125675f14be6a3c4c083e0ffde2","tid":446991,"uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":191,"score":-184,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:37:34.000Z","msg":"個廣告只係搞笑下姐，咁都可以鬧"},{"pid":"e0e20f3e879abce0b85cb816ae46ea8bf106daa7","tid":446991,"uid":63154,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:38:45.000Z","msg":"食完藥都一樣要請假休息，係個廣告鼓吹死頂咋"},{"pid":"fcb0dd7dfb169c4b57115c324624bb4f47c3b524","tid":446991,"uid":34377,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:40:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個廣告只係搞笑下姐，咁都可以鬧</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n撚屌賤種"},{"pid":"7031d03c844a293cdeb52a51dbbb45c23f9947b9","tid":446991,"uid":6038,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-